---
import "./CardDrivesWork1.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-questions" role="img" aria-label="Five interconnected nodes pulsing in sequence, suggesting a constellation of hard questions being examined">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" aria-hidden="true">
      <line x1="70" y1="50" x2="160" y2="90" />
      <line x1="250" y1="50" x2="160" y2="90" />
      <line x1="70" y1="130" x2="160" y2="90" />
      <line x1="250" y1="130" x2="160" y2="90" />
      <line x1="70" y1="50" x2="70" y2="130" />
      <line x1="250" y1="50" x2="250" y2="130" />
      <circle class="node n1" cx="70" cy="50" r="6" />
      <circle class="node n2" cx="250" cy="50" r="6" />
      <circle class="node n3" cx="160" cy="90" r="9" />
      <circle class="node n4" cx="70" cy="130" r="6" />
      <circle class="node n5" cx="250" cy="130" r="6" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="text-3 lh-2 fw-6">The questions we work on</h3>
    <p class="text-1 mt-2">What makes AI useful? What makes it a reliable actor? What is at the frontier today, and what are the signals? What creates impact that will outlive us?</p>
    <p class="text-1 mt-2">These questions shape every engagement we take on.</p>
  </div>
</article>
